    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Web Lab 2 Predict Level\r\n\r\nThis is an example of a predict level with multiple choice options.\r\n\r\nWhat will happen when you click on the 'Click me' button? Submit your answer and then try it out!",
